												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The player stops, confused, as Halsin comes lurching towards them from the darkness of the undercity. He is bloodied, bruised, clutching a wound on his side - something terrible has happened to him. In the distance, we hear a strange giggle (Orin - emote recorded within Nested dialogue)."
